{"tid":1991140,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"約翰遜：英國疫情已過高峰 醫療系統未有遭到癱瘓","createTime":"2020-04-27T08:31:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-27T09:03:07.000Z","uid":166360,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"8a6d249ce6c36f8b5738733ec2a5069c588e79d3","tid":1991140,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T08:31:23.000Z","msg":"約翰遜：英國疫情已過高峰 醫療系統未有遭到癱瘓<br />\n2020-04-27 HKT 16:23<br />\n<br />\n英國首相約翰遜恢復工作，他在唐寧街首相府外發表談話。<br />\n<br />\n約翰遜表示，已經達致管控疫情的第一項任務，避免英國的醫療系統遭到癱瘓，但他同時重申，必須要承認有另一波爆發的風險。<br />\n<br />\n約翰遜認為，英國的疫情已過高峰，但促請民眾繼續保持耐心，只要維持現時的做法，相信最終可以克服疫情。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1522978-20200427.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1522978-20200427.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=WEVEcTK9c1gYxUU7eN%2BS4TyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=27401757\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1522978-20200427.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=adb269b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1522978-20200427.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\nGod Save the Queen!  God Save the UK!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86fc2efc37a52bbeb45f14dfbed0f118289b1020","tid":1991140,"uid":759,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T08:33:12.000Z","msg":"希望復發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75183fbb5750068d8637cf8bcdc8ef88372f9f3a","tid":1991140,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T08:33:59.000Z","msg":"佢肯定⋯⋯⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"398b27081c9ac5de7d73e47012fb94c990ffd687","tid":1991140,"uid":57996,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T08:34:12.000Z","msg":"152840確診, 死左 20732人 <img src=\"/assets/fac